      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people care, but that feels so irrelevant right now. it’s not about wanting support, it’s just that it feels like i’ve reached the end of what a human is supposed to endure. like i’ve hit a wall that everything else just bounces off of. it feels more like a fact than a feeling, you know? that i'm just done.",
